Module mesakit.map.geography
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.geography.indexing.polygon

Class Node

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.map.geography.indexing.polygon.Node
public class Node extends Object
An interior Node of the spatial index that contains up to four quadrant objects, each of which could be another Node, a Leaf or null (if the quadrant is outside the polygon).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
